N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 19 ยง 206.10 - Other disciplinary and supervisory authority

State Regulations

Nothing in these rules shall be construed to limit the
authority of the Commission to supervise and discipline licensees, permit
holders, or otherwise authorized persons and entities, in its discretion
pursuant to law. Notes
